aws		lokal constant likelihood model (includes heteroskedastic case)
aws.gaussian	lokal constant Gaussian model including variance estimation (as f(mean))
aws.segment 	lokal constant Gaussian model/Segmentation
aws.irreg	lokal constant Gaussian model including variance estimation (as f(mean)) Irregular design (1D, 2D)
lpaws		local polynomial Gaussian models (1D or 2D grid, up to degree 2)
gkernsm		Nonadaptive Gaussian filter on a 1D, 2D or 3D grid using fft and mirroring
glmaws          Generalized linear models (in preparation)